{"lemma":"جَنابِ","slug":"جَنابِ","root":"ج.ن.ب","root_slug":"ج-ن-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ن-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6422","n6424","n6431"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَنَبَ (janaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a title of respect","examples":[{"text":"جَنَابْكُمْ","english":"your Honor"}]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Chenab (a river in Pakistan)","examples":[{"text":"وعوام الناس نهر راوي ونهر جناب ونهر هندوس"},{"text":"فلم يجد بدا من مفارقة وجهه فنهض في أواخر جمادی الاخرى ومعه اخوته وعبر نهر لوهور وسلك الطريق الى ان نزل على نهر جناب"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Urdu چَنَاب (canāb), ultimately from Sanskrit चन्द्रभागा (candrabhāgā)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒi.naːb/","/d͡ʒa.naːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6422","headword_ar":"جَنَابٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobN","text_ar":"جَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places. [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA Eanohumo janaAbayoni","text_ar":"كُنَّا عَنْهُمْ جَنَابَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbFA","text_ar":"جَنَابًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were remote,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired, from them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out of their way."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, (S, A, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibN","text_ar":"جَانِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an open or a wide space in front of a house or extending from its sides:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a settlement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of settling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mansion; an abode; a habitation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place to which a man betakes himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repairs, for lodging, covert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refuge, in a city or town or village or other place of settled habitations;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHolN","text_ar":"رَحْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vicinage, neighbourhood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract adjacent to the place of abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settlement, of a people"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonibapN","text_ar":"اَجْنِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA fiY janaAbi zayodK","text_ar":"اَنَا فِى جَنَابِ زَيْدٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am in the court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard, of Zeyd;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his place of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settlement."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN raHobu AljanaAbi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ رَحْبُ الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSiybu AljanaAbi","text_ar":"خَصِيبُ الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) the former meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is possessed of an ample"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mansion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., as explained above]: (TA:) [and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one is surrounded by a plentiful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruitful, tract:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or both mean (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one is generous"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bountiful"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hospitable"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaAnN jadiybu AljanaAbi","text_ar":"فَلَانٌ جَدِيبُ الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is environed by a tract affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"barrenness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as explained in the S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jdb","text_ar":"جدب"},{"kind":"text","text":": but generally used tropically, as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one is ungenerous, illiberal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inhospitable"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoSaba","text_ar":"اَخْصَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAbu Alqawomi","text_ar":"جَنَابُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The neighbourhood of the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tract surrounding them, became plentiful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruitful"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajodaba binaA AljanaAbu","text_ar":"اَجْدَبَ بِنَا الجَنَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our neighbourhood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tract surrounding us, became affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"barrenness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA from a trad.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN lay~inu AljanaAbi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ لَيِّنُ الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljaAnibi","text_ar":"الجَانِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man easy to deal with, compliant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obsequious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljanaAbu","text_ar":"الجَنَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a title often given by writers of letters and the like to any great man to whom others betake themselves, or repair, for protection; and sometimes to God; meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The object of recourse; the refuge; the asylum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaDorapu","text_ar":"الحَضْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., and used in the same manner, i. e., alone, and, without the article, prefixed to the name of the person to whom it is applied, or to a pronoun; but the latter is generally considered as implying greater respect than the former.]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6424","headword_ar":"جِنَابٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cord tied to the head and neck of a beast, by which he is led,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawn."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN TawoEu AljanaAbi","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ طَوْعُ الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse easily led;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to be led; tractable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obedient to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jnAb","text_ar":"جناب"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (S, A, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawoEu Aljanabi","text_ar":"طَوْعُ الجَنَبِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [See 1, near the beginning.])"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6431","headword_ar":"جُنَّابٌ","root":"jnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiybN","text_ar":"جَنِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}